{"tid":290815,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港男服「偉哥」潛入屋強姦前女友,被判囚11年","createTime":"2017-06-20T05:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T05:26:02.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49042240ed6d62f0af1db12aefcfa13d4d2c83dc","tid":290815,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T05:20:39.000Z","msg":"名男售貨員與前女友復合不果，之後躲於對方家中衣櫃內並服用壯陽藥，之後再伺機撲出強姦對方。29歲早前被裁定嚴重入屋犯法罪及強姦罪成，昨被判囚11年。<br />\n<br />\n法官判刑時指，本案情節異常惡劣，斥被告陳俊文早有預謀，又因怕被女事主見到自己而躲於衣櫃內。被告於強姦過程中又使用暴力，從控方的相片見到事主全身滿佈瘀傷，而被告更亮出鎅刀威脅事主，強迫在性交過程中不使用安全措施。<br />\n<br />\n法官又指，被告在犯案前服食壯陽藥為加重刑責的因素，指被告明顯有預謀犯案。<br />\n<br />\n法官透露，事主到現在仍經常想起案發情節，對她來說是不可磨滅的陰影，而審訊過程中亦見不到被告有任何悔意，或對事主有憐憫之心，最後判被告入獄11年<br />\n<a href=\"http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20170620/1/10/1/%E9%A3%9F%E6%9C%8D%E5%A3%AF%E9%99%BD%E8%97%A5%E5%8C%BF%E5%89%8D%E5%BA%A6%E8%A1%A3%E6%AB%83%E6%92%B2%E5%87%BA%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E5%94%AE%E8%B2%A8%E5%93%A1%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A11%E5%B9%B4-7574178.html?google_editors_picks=true&amp;google_editors_picks=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20170620%2F1%2F10%2F1%2F%25E9%25A3%259F%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%25A3%25AF%25E9%2599%25BD%25E8%2597%25A5%25E5%258C%25BF%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E6%25AB%2583%25E6%2592%25B2%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25A7%25A6-%25E5%2594%25AE%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A11%25E5%25B9%25B4-7574178.html%3Fgoogle_editors_picks%3Dtrue%26google_editors_picks%3Dtrue&d=P3Ct9nB%2Fhxif4vCYrtChYrr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=98092e68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20170620/1/10/1/%E9%A3%9F%E6%9C%8D%E5%A3%AF%E9%99%BD%E8%97%A5%E5%8C%BF%E5%89%8D%E5%BA%A6%E8%A1%A3%E6%AB%83%E6%92%B2%E5%87%BA%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E5%94%AE%E8%B2%A8%E5%93%A1%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A11%E5%B9%B4-7574178.html?google_editors_picks=true&amp;google_editors_picks=true</a><br />\n可能拍拖時無得扑 分手後強姦報復"},{"pid":"9dc88482e0eec1934f7bd2be9406bfeffe3b6d8a","tid":29081